00:31:13.210 --> 00:31:13.280
Who is this woman?

00:31:13.280 --> 00:31:15.610
♪ You just wait and see ♪

00:31:15.790 --> 00:31:16.850
She's my relative.

00:31:18.220 --> 00:31:19.880
Who are you trying to deceive?

00:31:20.270 --> 00:31:21.750
I heard her call Jin Zhao.

00:31:21.990 --> 00:31:23.280
No, she didn't.

00:31:23.750 --> 00:31:25.310
You misheard, Miss.

00:31:27.570 --> 00:31:28.570
Be honest with me.

00:31:29.280 --> 00:31:30.950
Is she Jin Zhao's new girl?

00:31:31.600 --> 00:31:33.000
How could that be possible?

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:34.330
You know him.

00:31:34.500 --> 00:31:36.100
