00:33:56.660 --> 00:33:58.080
Do you find it hard to understand

00:33:58.080 --> 00:34:00.320
why I care so much about your affairs?

00:34:03.050 --> 00:34:04.340
Maybe in your eyes,

00:34:05.580 --> 00:34:07.510
I'm just your childhood playmate,

00:34:08.650 --> 00:34:09.850
Coming here this time

00:34:10.170 --> 00:34:11.530
was just for fun.

00:34:11.620 --> 00:34:12.889
After the trip, I would leave

00:34:12.889 --> 00:34:14.620
and have nothing to do with you.

00:34:20.199 --> 00:34:21.000
That's right.

00:34:25.110 --> 00:34:26.590
How could you understand?

00:34:29.130 --> 00:34:30.900
If you could, you wouldn't have

00:34:33.120 --> 00:34:33.520
stayed away for all these years

00:34:33.520 --> 00:34:34.260
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

00:34:34.260 --> 00:34:36.460
without coming back to see me even once.

